text: Nabii Saalic:yi maraw yoh warisay anu inni Rabbik baxxaqqa iyya sumaaqih bagul eneeh, usuk isi xaquk nubuwwannu yoh yeceek, toysa anu kay amri cineeh usuk yoo edde ruube diinii kee farmo sin gudduyse week, toysa kay digaalák iyyi yoo catelee? tokkel isin cakkķi gitak makot yoo beytaanam kee kayri gitak yoo tayxeereeniih yi meqe taama yok bayissaanaah fingissaanamak sa isin yoh osissaanam manton keenik iyye
